QThesia should be a port of Synthesia (a midi Play,
	with MIDI Keyboard support, to learn the Keys for a Song)

I can be used on Linux, Max OSX and later Windows.

for reading midifiles jdksmidi is used (https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/jdksmidi.git)
RtMidi (http://www.music.mcgill.ca/~gary/rtmidi/)

